  "body": "When replaying transaction in the block we execute all the transactions before it but also all the transactions after.\r\n\r\nInstead we can shorten the block to only include preceding transations like here:\r\n\r\n```\r\nTransaction transaction = block.Transactions.FirstOrDefault(t => t.Hash == txHash);\r\nif (transaction == null)\r\n{\r\n    return null;\r\n}\r\n\r\nint indexOfTx = Array.IndexOf(block.Transactions, transaction);\r\nblock.Body = block.Body.WithChangedTransactions(block.Transactions.Take(indexOfTx + 1).ToArray());\r\n```\r\n[ ] trace_replayTransaction\r\n[ ] trace_transaction\r\n[ ] GethSTyleTracer",
